instructions: put the plate in the center of the charger
put the napkin in the center of the plate with the ends pointing up and down
Put the dinner fork to the immediate left of the plate with the tines pointing up.
Put the salad fork to the left of the dinner fork with the tines pointing up.
Put the dinner knife to the right of the charger with the blade pointed up.
Put the teaspoon to the right of the dinner knife with the bowl pointed up.
Put the soup spoon to the right of the teaspoon with the bowl pointed up.
Put the water glass at the top right corner of the charger so that it's above and left of the knife.
Put the wine glass just to the right of the water glass.
Put a second wine glass under the first wine glass so that it's just above the two spoons.
Put a coffee cup to the right of the wine glasses and just above and to the right of the soup spoon,
Put the bread plate above the two forks and to the left of the charger.
Put the butter knife in the center of the bread plate with the blade pointed toward the water glass.
Put a dessert fork between the bread plate and the water glass, tines point to the water glass.
Put the dessert spoon between the dessert fork and the charger with the bowl to the bread plate.
